    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no major mechanical issues, though it may have minor wear items that could use attention over time. The exterior is in decent shape with only light cosmetic wear \u2014 small scuffs or minor blemishes may be present but nothing significant. The interior is clean and functional with normal use showing.",
