    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple visible dents, scratches, and areas of significant paint wear. The interior is heavily worn, with damaged seating surfaces and deteriorated trim pieces. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require repairs. Suitable for buyers who are comfortable taking on a project vehicle or need basic transportation and can handle the associated costs.",
